title: Propagate Actor snapshots through durable jobs retries and outbox
updated_at: "2026-07-12T17:00:40Z"
---
Acceptance: Durable jobs, retries, outbox entries, cancellation, and restart preserve the immutable initiating Actor snapshot and logical Principal/account lineage without tokens. Execution re-resolves current authority; stale, split, revoked, or mismatched lineage fails closed and never borrows another participant identity. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-13-github-user-attribution-and-feature-discovery.md.